      <p class="eyebrow">Who we are</p>
      <h2>Vertical transportation built around safety</h2>
      <p>Everest World Lifts was first incorporated as Everest Elevators Ltd in June 2006 under RC 656022. The company changed its name to Everest World Lifts Ltd in February 2019 and is registered under RC 1560172.</p>
      <p>From our Abuja base, we provide elevator, escalator, and moving walkway distribution, installation, preventive maintenance, repair, modernization, planning, and consulting services.</p>
      <p>We support clients from the early planning stage by helping determine appropriate equipment numbers, sizes, speeds, and system requirements for both present and future building needs.</p>
    </div>
